      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "The representations are not mutually exclusive. A common pattern: a hierarchical outer structure (phases) with a DAG inner structure within each phase. This gives human-readable phase grouping with intra-phase parallelism:"
          }
